title: Nevosoft - Anabel - New 3D Hidden Object Puzzle [h33t][Wendy99]
description:
A new 3D hidden object game and adventure of Nevosoft!


Translated from Russian with an electronic dictionary

You play the princess Anabel. Bad priest Amirtekh tries 
to catch her for the harem. But Anabel is fallen in love 
with prince Ikhnatona.

Anabel escapes, leaves the palace of the pharaoh, 
investigates the pyramid, visits an ancient Egyptian 
village, swims aboard a ship on the Nile and visits 
the temple of the omnipotent god Set. 

it&#039;s one of beautiful games recently,
dialogs are russian but substitles are english,
